Package jetbrains.mps.ide.editor

Interface NodeEditorFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeEditorFactoryBase, TabsMPSEditorFactory
    public interface NodeEditorFactory
    Factory to instantiate editor for a node. It's EditorOpenHandler done right - no IOperationContext, and it doesn't open editors, it instantiates (hence factory) component, and actual code to open an editor is platform's responsibility.

    Instances of the factory are registered with EXT_POINT extension point, within Project area (thus can access Project or MPSProject as constructor argument.

    To avoid code breakage in the future MPS versions, do not implement this interface directly (outside of MPS), rather subclass NodeEditorFactoryBase.

    Since:
    3.4
